data.description: ***Buyer is a 504 Contingency; Please continue to show and offer*** Presenting a fantastic opportunity to own this immaculate, ''like-new'' residence with 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, ready for immediate occupancy and eagerly awaiting its new owners. Enjoy the convenience of numerous upgraded features, such as Ethernet drops in all rooms, an impressive 11-foot ceiling height in the living area, and 9-foot ceilings throughout the remaining areas on the main level. Take delight in the expansive 14x15 covered back porch, providing a perfect setting for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. This home has been designed with energy efficiency and low maintenance in mind, allowing you to spend your days relishing the abundant amenities offered by the community. Take advantage of the nearby golf course, swimming pool, clubhouse, fitness center, and bocce ball area, adding a vibrant and active dimension to your lifestyle. Conveniently located near shopping, entertainment and I-20! Don't miss the chance to make this your new cherished haven!
